Minting this special 1/1 unique item for my friend and collector: CIRCLEMAN
Cirleman is a generous philanthropist who is always there to encourage those who work hard and have the heart at the right place. That's because he, himself doesn't like to work hard. Not because he is lazy but because he is smart. He knows life fully enjoyed in the moment is better than on spent in a perpetual rush of distractions. 

His actions, even without any effort has ripple effects stronger than thousands tsunamis. His impact will be remembered for ever until the cold death of the universe. Many would not hesitate to call him a good Samaritan, but he is Egyptian. 

Even if it's too far... let's go there !
